  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the analgesic efficacy of Egalet-002 twice daily
      (BID) in patients with moderate-to-severe chronic low back pain
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
